'''West African Insurance Institute''' is a sub regional insurance education centre in [[Banjul]], [[The Gambia]].<ref name="kinmp">{{cite web | url=http://www.accessgambia.com/extra/waii-west-african-insurance-institute.html | title=West African Insurance Institute (WAII Gambia) | publisher=www.accessgambia.com | accessdate=18 July 2013}}</ref> The institute trains and certifies insurers from [[West Africa]] and offers them certificates.<ref name="hilp">{{cite web | url=http://www.ghanabizmedia.com/ghanabizmedia/december-2012-insurance/876-regional-insurance-industrys-strides-and-challenges.html | title=Regional insurance industry's strides and challenges | publisher=ghanabizmedia.com | accessdate=18 July 2013}}</ref> It was established in 1973.<ref name="iuhiu">{{cite web | url=http://acronyms.thefreedictionary.com/West+African+Insurance+Institute | title=West african institute | publisher=thefreedictionary.com | accessdate=18 July 2013}}</ref>

